    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-06-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-06-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="987"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d987">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 891.51/71.</note>
                <head>[Extract]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-06-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 13, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 132.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I inclose a translation of an act of the
                        Medjles<note n="1" xml:id="d987fn1">Not printed.</note> passed to-day,
                    giving full powers in financial matters or Treasury business to Mr. Shuster.
                    This was passed by an almost unanimous vote. Little overt opposition.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Charles W. Russell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
